                    Responsive image
                  </h3>
                </div>
                <div
                  class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 sm:p-6"
                >
                  <div class="relative">
  <div id="pane" class="overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="images/grid-image/image-01.png"
